{"type": "article", "id": 23528, "title": "多功能公共设施", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-09T07:30:19Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 36, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702135007cz5w4Cvq0YOPtfan.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是一个放在公共场所的设施，结合了桌椅、垃圾桶和自行车停放架。设计师利用废弃的铁架和木材，将它们整合成屏风一样的装置里，是连贯的。放在大树下面有保护树木的作用，也能成为一个景观。产品目前还是概念，但提供一种重新思考公共设施设计的角度。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702135005ifCdLFvQzypmUxHt.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.70952381\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702135006tdmHlFhkNfcBq5Yn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65142857\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702135006B6S4rfQdKm5A8taL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.76666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}